skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: depression checker
des:
It use phq-9 depression checker questionnaire to evaluate the level of depression in user using this skill.'
The level can be normal, mild ,moderate, severely moderate and severe.
It does not store the user data it only takes data and use with ai-ml model to predict depression that mode is hosted on aws lambda
